cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with tasks involving images and language, such as image captioning and textual entailment. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computer Science related to Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Computer Vision (cs.CV), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper also discusses hypernym prediction and image-caption retrieval, which are tasks related to Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
